\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span>  <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Category<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 2 <\/span>"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Language":[],"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"font-size:19px;\">Based on everything you have reviewed, <b>which product would you purchase<\/b>?<\/span>","QuestionID":"QID18"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID19","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-size:19px;\">Based on everything you have reviewed, <b>which product would you purchase<\/b>?<\/span>","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Beats Fit Pro ($159.99)"},"2":{"Display":"JBL Endurance Race ($49.99)"},"3":{"Display":"Shokz OpenRun Pro 2 ($179.99)"},"4":{"Display":"Vynex OpenReal ($39.99)"},"5":{"Display":"Sony WF-SP800N ($129.99)"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Randomization":{"Type":"All","Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":""},"DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"LogicType":"EmbeddedField","LeftOperand":"Category","Operator":"EqualTo","RightOperand":"3","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span>  <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Category<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 3 <\/span>"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Language":[],"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"font-size:19px;\">Based on everything you have reviewed, <b>which product would you purchase<\/b>?<\/span>","QuestionID":"QID19"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID2","SecondaryAttribute":"School of Marketing and International Business CONSENT FORM -- PROLIFIC Study Title: \"Consumer De...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h3><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">School of Marketing and International Business<br \/>\nCONSENT FORM -- PROLIFIC<br \/>\n<br \/>\nStudy Title: &quot;Consumer Decision Making Study&quot;<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Background Information<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nWe are inviting you to be part of a research study about how consumers evaluate product information and make purchasing decisions. We seek to understand how people use product comparison information to choose products. This form will tell you what the study is about, what we will ask you to do, and how your information will be used. Please read this carefully. Feel free to ask questions if you don&#39;t understand something. Taking part in this study is completely your choice. You can decide not to join, or if you join, you can stop at any time. There is no punishment or penalty if you decide not to take part or if you quit later.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThis study is being conducted by:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThis study is being done by Felipe M. Affonso from School of Marketing and International Business at Oklahoma State University.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Procedures<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nIf you decide to join, we will ask you to:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nFill out a survey about consumer product evaluation and decision making. You will state your product preferences, view product comparison information, make a product selection, and answer questions about your decision.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIt will take about 6 minutes.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Benefits and Risks of being in the Study<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nYou may not get direct benefits from this study, but your participation could help researchers learn more about consumer decision-making and help others in the future.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThis study involves the following risks:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThere are no risks in this study that are greater than what you experience in daily life.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nWe will take steps to reduce these risks by:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIf any question makes you uncomfortable, you can skip it or choose to quit the study at any time.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Will You get Paid?<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nYou will be paid for taking part in the study. You will get compensation after you finish the study. You will be paid $0.20 per minute ($1.20 for a 6-minute survey). If the research team discovers that participants falsified their identity to meet eligibility criteria, the team reserves the right to dismiss the participant from the study and not pay them for participation.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nProlific does not allow for prorated compensation. In the event of an incomplete submission, you must contact the research team, and compensation will be determined based on what was completed and at the researchers&#39; discretion.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nPLEASE NOTE: This study contains a number of checks to make sure that participants are finishing the tasks honestly and completely. We are following Prolific&#39;s policies. As long as you read the instructions and complete the tasks, your submission will be approved. If you fail these checks, your submission will be rejected.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nApproved: <\/span><\/span>04\/09\/2026<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Protocol #: <\/span><\/span>IRB-26-175<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><strong>How Will Your Information Be Kept Private?<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe information you share in this study will be anonymous. This means your name will not be collected or connected to your answers. Once you finish the study, we will not be able to remove your data because it will not be linked to you.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nYour Prolific ID will be used to distribute payment to you, but will not be stored with the research data we collect from you.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe research team will do its best to keep your information private, using the technology available. However, because you are answering online, there is a small chance that someone who is not supposed to could see your answers. This risk is similar to what you might face when using the internet in daily life. If you have concerns, you can check the privacy policy of the online provider here: www.qualtrics.com\/privacy-statement\/<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>How Your Information Will Be Collected and Stored?<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nWe will collect your information using surveys using the Qualtrics survey software. Your information will be stored in:<br \/>\n<br \/>\n- Qualtrics Servers (encrypted and password-protected)<br \/>\n- Local data files (encrypted and password-protected on a hard drive inside the University)<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Contacts and Questions<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe Institutional Review Board (IRB) for the protection of human research participants at Oklahoma State University has reviewed and approved this study. If you have questions about the research study itself, please contact the Principal Investigator at (405) 744-1311, felipe.affonso@okstate.edu. If you have questions about your rights as a research volunteer or would simply like to speak with someone other than the research team about concerns regarding this study, please contact the IRB at (405) 744-3377 or irb@okstate.edu. All reports or correspondence will be kept confidential.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Statement of Consent<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nI have read this form and understand what the study is about. I have had the chance to ask questions. By signing this, I agree to take part in the study.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIf you agree to join the study, please click I agree and continue.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nApproved: <\/span><\/span>04\/09\/2026<br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Protocol #: <\/span><\/span>IRB-26-175<br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/h3>","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I agree"},"2":{"Display":"I do not agree"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"DataExportTag":"consent","QuestionID":"QID2","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionDescription":"School of Marketing and International Business CONSENT FORM -- PROLIFIC Study Title: \"Consumer De...","NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function(){\n  var tables = document.querySelectorAll('table');\n  tables.forEach(function(table){\n    var tbody = table.querySelector('tbody');\n    if (!tbody) {\n      var rows = Array.from(table.querySelectorAll('tr'));\n      if (rows.length > 1) {\n        tbody = document.createElement('tbody');\n        for (var i = 1; i < rows.length; i++) {\n          tbody.appendChild(rows[i]);\n        }\n        table.appendChild(tbody);\n      }\n    }\n    if (tbody) {\n      var rows = Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr'));\n      for (var i = rows.length - 1; i > 0; i--) {\n        var j = Math.floor(Math.random() * (i + 1));\n        var temp = rows[i];\n        rows[i] = rows[j];\n        rows[j] = temp;\n      }\n      rows.forEach(function(row){ tbody.appendChild(row); });\n\n      \/\/ Record the shuffled order\n      var brandOrder = rows.map(function(row){\n        var firstCell = row.querySelector('td');\n        return firstCell ? firstCell.textContent.trim() : '?';\n      });\n      Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('ProductDisplayOrder', brandOrder.join('|'));\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\n});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID20","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":3,"MaxSeconds":"0"},"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"Language":[],"DataExportTag":"timer_wtp","QuestionID":"QID20"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID21","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-size:19px;\">What is the <b>maximum amount<\/b> you would be willing to pay for the product you just chose?<br><br><span style=\"font-size:15px; color:#666;\">Please enter a dollar amount (e.g., 75). Think about what this product is genuinely worth to you, not what it costs in the comparison table.<\/span><\/span>","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","MinChars":"1","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"0","Max":"500","NumDecimals":"2"}}},"Language":[],"DataExportTag":"wtp_chosen","QuestionID":"QID21"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID22","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":3,"MaxSeconds":"0"},"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"Language":[],"DataExportTag":"timer_confidence","QuestionID":"QID22"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3PHq8N243mxAr0W","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID23","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"Ques